      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minor signs of wear consistent with careful ownership. While there may be a few small cosmetic imperfections, it remains a reliable and attractive option for anyone seeking a dependable, well-cared-for car.",
