    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a solid project or budget-friendly option for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows noticeable signs of age, including several paint chips and a few minor dents on the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat. While it starts and runs, the engine could use a tune-up, and the tires will likely need replacing within the next few months. It is a reliable runner for now, but a thorough inspection and some TLC will be required to bring it back to its best.",
