      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and possessing a documented history of fastidious care. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a commitment to preservation, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from a new delivery. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly peerless example of the marque.",
