    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. This car is in showroom condition, featuring original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no chips, swirls, or scratches. The interior is equally flawless; the premium upholstery shows no signs of use, the dash and trim are free of any UV fading, and the cabin retains its original fresh scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is perfect, supported by a full binder of service records documenting preventative maintenance performed strictly by certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is entirely free of surface rust or road grime. It sits on a fresh set of premium tires and includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of this model.",
